column1: # 000 - rjd - time of observation in Reduced Julian date
# 001 - bjd - time of observation in Baryocentric Julian date
# 002 - net - network of telescopes observing this target
# 003 - stf - station ID of the telescope observing this target
# 008 - flt - filter ID from the filters table
# 009 - xcc - x coordinate on CCD chip
# 010 - ycc - y coordinate on CCD chip
# 011 - bgv - sky background measurement around object in ADU
# 012 - bge - error in sky background measurement in ADU
# 013 - fsv - source extraction S parameter (the PSF spatial RMS)
# 014 - fdv - source extraction D parameter (the PSF spatial ellipticity in xy)
# 015 - fkv - source extraction K parameter (the PSF spatial diagonal ellipticity)
# 016 - aim_000 - aperture photometry raw instrumental magnitude in aperture 000
# 017 - aie_000 - aperture photometry raw instrumental mag error in aperture 000
